          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>plant-based curried cauliflower cheeze</strong> with the <strong>Bombay potatoes </strong>and <strong>dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
